      "content": "exactly. it's just a heavy, empty feeling. like, if there's no inherent point to any of this, then isn't there a certain kind of peace in just accepting that? instead of fighting against the void and pretending there's a reason to keep struggling, isn't it more logical to just... stop? to stop participating in a game that has no winner and no meaning?",
